### Hadith 3:435

*Narrated Zaid bin Khalid and Abu Huraira:*

that Allah's Apostle was asked about an unmarried slave-girl who
committed illegal sexual intercourse. They heard him saying, "Flog her,
and if she commits illegal sexual intercourse after that, flog her
again, and on the third (or the fourth) offense, sell her."

